406
00:26:40,540 --> 00:26:41,810
Compensation?

407
00:26:42,300 --> 00:26:43,220
I don’t give a toss.

408
00:26:43,810 --> 00:26:44,530
We’ve been running

409
00:26:44,550 --> 00:26:46,230
