416
00:27:00,180 --> 00:27:01,260
I have to meet Shan Junhao.

417
00:27:03,430 --> 00:27:04,180
Stop him!

418
00:27:05,140 --> 00:27:05,800
Mr. Tang!

419
00:27:12,650 --> 00:27:13,130
Mr. Tang!

420
00:27:13,640 --> 00:27:14,220
Mr. Tang!

