490
00:29:45,780 --> 00:29:46,580
Mr. Shan.

491
00:29:47,890 --> 00:29:48,700
Junhao.

492
00:29:52,520 --> 00:29:53,810
Shan Junhao!

493
00:29:53,830 --> 00:29:54,510
It’s me.

494
00:29:55,400 --> 00:29:56,340
Because of you,

495
00:29:56,950 --> 00:29:58,600
