00:33:26,210 --> 00:33:27,500
Don’t give yourself too much pressure.

572
00:33:27,800 --> 00:33:29,730
In fact, according to our Credit Agreement,

573
00:33:29,750 --> 00:33:31,760
if you can raise enough money in a month

574
00:33:31,780 --> 00:33:32,640
and pay the debt,

575
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:34,320
you’re given preferential right

576
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:36,190
to buy Guanmei Hotel’s shares.

577
00:33:40,330 --> 00:33:41,330
A month?

578
00:33:44,950 --> 00:33:45,950
It won’t help.

579
00:33:48,190 --> 00:33:48,800
He’s in.

580
00:33:50,910 --> 00:33:53,130
Tang! Tang!

581
00:33:53,570 --> 00:33:54,740
Tang, are you alright?

582
00:33:56,110 --> 00:33:57,030
Yes.

583
00:33:57,050 --> 00:33:58,020
I’m fine, Qianyu.

584
00:34:03,920 --> 00:34:05,150
Why do you do that?

585
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:08,000
Guanmei Hotel means nothing to you.

586
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:09,650
But to Tang,

587
00:34:09,670 --> 00:34:11,140
it’s everything.

588
00:34:15,040 --> 00:34:16,460
Different stances. No explanation.

589
00:34:18,210 --> 00:34:19,430
I just want to say

590
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:20,830
sorry.

591
00:34:21,630 --> 00:34:22,090
I…

592
00:34:22,110 --> 00:34:24,040
All right, Qianyu.

593
00:34:24,560 --> 00:34:26,180
It really has nothing

594
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:28,070
to do with Director Xu.

595
00:34:31,020 --> 00:34:31,940
OK, Tang.

596
00:34:32,260 --> 00:34:33,200
Let’s go home.

597
00:34:36,840 --> 00:34:37,590
OK.

598
00:35:36,080 --> 00:35:36,550
Hi!

599
00:35:36,570 --> 00:35:38,390
We do not buy at this door.

600
00:35:38,410 --> 00:35:39,620
We don’t need anything, either.

601
00:35:40,020 --> 00:35:41,730
Toilet on the outside to the right.

602
00:35:41,910 --> 00:35:44,410
Our toilet is open to customers only.

603
00:35:44,430 --> 00:35:45,590
No, I’m…

604
00:35:45,610 --> 00:35:47,460
We don’t need extra hands, either.

605
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:49,500
The old house is going to be demolished.

606
00:35:49,700 --> 00:35:51,630
We’re about to lose our jobs.

607
00:35:54,040 --> 00:35:55,160
I want to say that

608
00:35:55,620 --> 00:35:56,900
I need a room.

609
00:35:57,620 --> 00:35:58,480
A room?

610
00:35:59,360 --> 00:36:00,470
You want a room?

611
00:36:01,940 --> 00:36:03,200
Nice to meet you.

612
00:36:03,220 --> 00:36:04,090
Welcome!

613
00:36:04,110 --> 00:36:06,500
Can you tell me what kind of room do you prefer?

614
00:36:06,720 --> 00:36:07,320
Let me help.

615
00:36:08,870 --> 00:36:10,310
But you said that

616
00:36:11,040 --> 00:36:12,200
it’s gonna be demolished.

617
00:36:13,090 --> 00:36:13,730
Yes.

618
00:36:14,150 --> 00:36:15,720
You’d better go to the downtown…

619
00:36:15,900 --> 00:36:17,040
It’s not demolished yet.

620
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:21,600
Do you want a business suite, standard room,

621
00:36:21,620 --> 00:36:22,640
or VIP suite?

622
00:36:22,660 --> 00:36:24,850
Can I take a look of the room first?

623
00:36:25,100 --> 00:36:25,880
Of course.

624
00:36:25,900 --> 00:36:26,720
I’ll show you the way. Come along.

625
00:36:26,740 --> 00:36:27,550
This way please.

626
00:36:28,220 --> 00:36:28,700
Please.

627
00:36:36,470 --> 00:36:37,780
Sir, come in.

628
00:36:39,430 --> 00:36:40,960
In Guanmei Fishing Village,

629
00:36:40,980 --> 00:36:42,310
our hotel is…

630
00:36:44,240 --> 00:36:46,760
Every book and every object here

631
00:36:46,780 --> 00:36:49,110
have their special meaning and story.

632
00:36:50,360 --> 00:36:50,950
Sir,

633
00:36:51,340 --> 00:36:53,200
on the upstairs is your bedroom.

634
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:54,620
By the way,

635
00:36:54,890 --> 00:36:55,900
the most noted feature

636
00:36:56,100 --> 00:36:57,630
of our hotel is that

637
00:36:58,370 --> 00:37:00,320
you can see the ocean in the day

638
00:37:00,340 --> 00:37:01,890
and watch stars at night.

639
00:37:05,350 --> 00:37:06,410
Too dusty.

640
00:37:07,590 --> 00:37:08,390
Excuse us.

641
00:37:08,410 --> 00:37:09,860
It’s a sea view room. Wind is strong.

642
00:37:15,140 --> 00:37:16,140
Gosh!

643
00:37:23,370 --> 00:37:24,050
What’s up?

644
00:37:25,950 --> 00:37:27,550
I want some excise.

645
00:37:28,040 --> 00:37:28,970
I like excise.

646
00:37:29,890 --> 00:37:30,640
Sports.

647
00:37:30,660 --> 00:37:31,370
We love sports.

648
00:37:31,390 --> 00:37:32,370
I love sports, too.

649
00:37:33,440 --> 00:37:37,050
So, sir, how do you like the room?

650
00:37:37,070 --> 00:37:38,540
Great, this is it.

651
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:40,960
Here.

652
00:37:42,990 --> 00:37:43,630
Check me in.

653
00:37:45,400 --> 00:37:46,660
I’ll get it done now.

654
00:37:54,670 --> 00:37:56,420
He’s been to so many countries.

655
00:37:56,760 --> 00:37:58,560
Goodness!

656
00:38:03,980 --> 00:38:06,420
I never expected that before we make a move,

657
00:38:06,570 --> 00:38:09,470
Shan Junhao came a cropper.

658
00:38:10,470 --> 00:38:11,680
But it’s great.

659
00:38:12,510 --> 00:38:14,380
Saved us the trouble.

660
00:38:17,280 --> 00:38:19,370
That’s the consequence of his rash decision.

661
00:38:20,190 --> 00:38:22,900
He urged to advance
Guanmei Fishing Village project

662
00:38:23,430 --> 00:38:25,350
and got Tang Shuming here.

663
00:38:27,290 --> 00:38:29,150
Each of Shan Junhao’s mistakes

664
00:38:29,480 --> 00:38:32,240
will become our trump card.

665
00:38:52,240 --> 00:38:57,330
♪ Distance between us ♪

666
00:39:00,530 --> 00:39:05,610
♪ Seems short yet long ♪

667
00:39:06,660 --> 00:39:10,740
♪ Heartfelt words are exchanged in diaries ♪

668
00:39:10,760 --> 00:39:14,390
♪ There are no secrets between us ♪

669
00:39:14,940 --> 00:39:22,310
♪ Didn’t get to say I love you so much ♪

670
00:39:23,640 --> 00:39:27,760
♪ You broke into my lonely heart ♪

671
00:39:27,920 --> 00:39:31,620
♪ And lit the fire called love ♪

672
00:39:31,970 --> 00:39:36,150
♪ You drove out all my loneliness ♪

673
00:39:36,170 --> 00:39:39,580
♪ So that I can slowly adjust myself ♪

674
00:39:40,200 --> 00:39:44,290
♪ You painted my life ♪

675
00:39:44,420 --> 00:39:47,930
♪ With flowers ♪

676
00:39:47,950 --> 00:39:51,970
♪ You raised me up ♪

677
00:39:51,990 --> 00:39:55,340
♪ From that moment on ♪

678
00:39:55,880 --> 00:39:58,620
♪ You’ve been singing for me ♪
